OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain will soon clear east then
OL,6,Fsunny spells and showers. Drier for a
OL,7,Ftime in the afternoon before further
OL,8,Fshowers later, heavy at times. Cool
OL,9,Fand blustery.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FScattered to frequent
OL,12,Fblustery showers feed in from the west
OL,13,Fthrough the evening and overnight,
OL,14,Fthese showers heavy at times. Staying
OL,15,Fdriest in eastern Borders.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FIt will be quite cool with
OL,18,Fbright or sunny spells and scattered
OL,19,Fheavy showers. Blustery winds around
OL,20,Fthe southwest coast. Chance of
OL,21,Fovernight frost in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
